Using the plugin: 

All you have to do to use this plugin is select the element that contains a set of links which link to image files.

For example:
------------

<div class="thumbs">
    
    <a href="/path_to_image/filename.jpg" title="This is the image title">

</div>

----------

Add a tooltip to show the image like this:

-------

$(function() {
    $('.thumbs').TipItUp();

    // customize options support:
    $('.thumbs').TipItUp({
        offset: 20; // offset from mouse position
        speed: 50; // fade in speed
        delay: 100; // delay before fade in
    });
});

